## Output Requirements

Your output MUST:

1. Use T001 format with checkbox syntax: `- [ ] T001 [Description]`
2. Group tasks into numbered phases matching the implementation plan
3. Mark parallel-safe tasks with [P]
4. Follow TDD order: test task BEFORE implementation task in each phase
5. Include exact file paths for every task
6. Include a Dependencies & Execution Order section
7. Include an Implementation Strategy section

